                        <note rend="inline" type="source">393.11/1107: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to the Consul General at Canton</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Jenkins</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1930-04-25T11:00:00-05:00">April 25, 1930—11
                                a.m.</date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>Your April 24, noon, last paragraph. Neither Department nor Catholic
                            authorities have information of later date.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Cotton</hi></signed></closer>
